title: Distribute NFT-Platform Fee to PanCakeSquad Holder
body: We need more usecases for the NFT's, one good option would be to distribute the NTF-Marketplace fee's to all holders. This way it wouldnt negatively affect the cake token since fee are distributed in BNB, and people proberbly even going buy $CAKE with the generated income, so might even benefit cake.
author: 0xf89b1a37e4FdcDa1722C9378FaAFf59794DEb803
